# AmmoOS Software Update — safe GitHub check from AmmoLang
@profile fastest
@verbose clean
@motto "AmmoOS update · preflight · GitHub · lock-safe"

seq ·
  say "Software Update Manager — AmmoLang preflight"
  self upgrade
  fast path:gpy fastest
  github check repo:ZacharyGeurts/AmmoOS
  update check
  say "Use /ammoos-update-os to apply when update_available"